name: Spacetronaut (Bryson_Frank, jliu2, NavHee)
description:
(Sound Warning)   You will float around space with the wasd keys, and point and click to shoot aliens and the members of the Evil & Villainous Cosmonauts company. The game is played like a top-down shooter except it is from a side view.
